        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued August 1 at 5:18PM MDT until August 1 at 5:45PM MDT by NWS Great Falls MT</headline>
        <description>At 518 PM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 9 miles south of
Moore, or 21 miles southwest of Lewistown, moving northeast at 10
mph.

HAZARD...Golf ball size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...People and animals outdoors will be injured. Expect damage
to roofs, siding, windows, and vehicles.

Locations impacted include...
Moore, Buffalo, and Garneill.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
